{
  "stanzas": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Now praise the hidden God of love"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "In whom we all must live and move,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "Who shepherds us, at every stage"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "Thro’ youth, maturity, and age."
        }
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Who challenged us, when were young"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "To storm the citadels of wrong;"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "In care for others taught us how"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "God’s true community must grow."
        }
      ],
      "number": 2
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Who bids us never lose our zest,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Tho’ age is urging us to rest,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "But proves to us that we have still"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "A work to do, a place to fill."
        }
      ],
      "number": 3
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Then talk no more of wasted time,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "But Godward look, and upward climb,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "Content to sleep, when day is done,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "And rise refreshed, and travel on."
        }
      ],
      "number": 4
    }
  ],
  "title": "Now Praise the Hidden God of Love"
}
